## 2. Required Scripts (`package.json`)

```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "lint": "eslint . --ext .ts,.tsx --max-warnings=0",
    "lint:fix": "eslint . --ext .ts,.tsx --fix",
    "format": "prettier --write \"**/*.{ts,tsx,json,md,yml,yaml}\"",
    "format:check": "prettier --check \"**/*.{ts,tsx,json,md,yml,yaml}\"",
    "typecheck": "tsc --noEmit",
    "test": "jest",
    "test:coverage": "jest --coverage",
    "codegen": "graphql-codegen --config codegen.yml",
    "codegen:watch": "graphql-codegen --config codegen.yml --watch",
    "codegen:check": "graphql-codegen --config codegen.yml --check",
    "validate": "npm run lint && npm run typecheck && npm run test -- --watchAll=false && npm run codegen:check"
  }
}
```

**`validate` script:** Runs all checks (used in CI)

