## 8. Testing Requirements

### 8.1 Coverage Thresholds

**jest.config.js:**
```javascript
module.exports = {
  coverageThreshold: {
    global: {
      branches: 70,
      functions: 70,
      lines: 70,
      statements: 70,
    },
  },
}
```

**What this means:**
- PRs that drop coverage below 70% fail CI
- Encourages comprehensive testing

---

### 8.2 Required Tests

**For new features:**
- [ ] Component integration tests (RTL)
- [ ] Happy path
- [ ] Error states
- [ ] Loading states
- [ ] Edge cases

**For bug fixes:**
- [ ] Regression test (reproduces bug, proves fix)

**See:** [04_frontend-testing-strategy.mdc](./04_frontend-testing-strategy.mdc)

