## 11. Deployment Pipeline (Separate from CI)

**CI:** Validate code quality (on every PR)
**CD:** Deploy to environments (on merge to specific branches)

**Trigger:** Merge to `main` or `develop`

**EAS Build + Deploy:**
```yaml
# .github/workflows/deploy.yml
name: Deploy

on:
  push:
    branches: [main]

jobs:
  deploy-preview:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - uses: expo/expo-github-action@v8
      - run: npm ci
      - run: eas build --profile preview --platform all --non-interactive
      - run: eas submit --platform ios --latest
```

**See:** [08_mobile-deployment.mdc](./08_mobile-deployment.mdc) for full deployment strategy.

