## 12. Performance & Bundle Size Checks

### 12.1 Bundle Size Monitoring

**GitHub Action:**
```yaml
- name: Analyze bundle size
  run: npx expo export:web --dump-sourcemap

- name: Check bundle size
  run: |
    SIZE=$(du -sh dist | cut -f1)
    echo "Bundle size: $SIZE"
    # Fail if bundle > 5MB (example threshold)
```

**Tools:**
- `@expo/webpack-config` — Bundler
- `source-map-explorer` — Visualize bundle composition

