## 16. Skipping Hooks (Discouraged)

**Emergency bypass:**
```bash
git commit --no-verify  # Skip pre-commit hooks
git push --no-verify    # Skip pre-push hooks
```

**❌ DO NOT use unless:**
- Reverting a broken commit
- Emergency hotfix (and CI still runs)

**Rule:** CI is the final authority. If CI fails, code doesn't merge.

